take you to dinner?

40:25.000 --> 40:27.750
♪ I don't know
what I believe in anymore ♪

40:27.750 --> 40:29.420
Okay.

40:29.420 --> 40:30.500
Okay.

40:30.500 --> 40:33.750
♪ Real change is hard ♪

40:33.750 --> 40:36.710
♪ I try not to freak out ♪

40:36.710 --> 40:41.040
♪ Try not to worry
about the future ♪

40:41.040 --> 40:45.000
♪♪

40:45.000 --> 40:48.460
I never fit in anywhere,
and I kept trying.

40:48.460 --> 40:50.420
I kept wanting to belong,
but nothing ever worked out,

40:50.420 --> 40:52.380
so I had to keep moving.

40:52.380 --> 40:54.830
Or maybe I was running
from my circumstances,

40:54.830 --> 40:56.040
running from myself,

40:56.040 --> 40:57.830
running from anyone
who dared to love me.

40:57.830 --> 41:00.120
Just give me a minute.
Just one second.

41:00.120 --> 41:01.210
Wait, Alex.

41:01.210 --> 41:02.880
It's right here.
I put it right here.

41:02.880 --> 41:04.120
No, Alex,
I'm still talking.

41:04.120 --> 41:05.500
Damn it,
it was just right here!

41:05.500 --> 41:06.960
Alex, I'm not done yet!

41:06.960 --> 41:08.790
Where the freak
is my ring?

41:08.790 --> 41:10.580
Alex, I'm wearing it!

41:10.580 --> 41:12.670
♪♪

41:12.670 --> 41:14.710
Meredith:
Scarred hearts don't heal.

41:14.710 --> 41:17.460
But over time,
the scars can change.

41:17.460 --> 41:21.540
♪♪

41:21.540 --> 41:23.460
I always thought that there was
something wrong with me,

41:23.460 --> 41:26.670
and I always wanted to run
until I met you.

41:26.670 --> 41:31.830
[ Laughing ] You're so screwed
up that you make me make sense.

41:31.830 --> 41:34.080
You and me.

41:34.080 --> 41:36.170
We just fit.

41:36.170 --> 41:39.170
And I don't want to leave you,
Alex.

41:39.170 --> 41:41.000
I want a great, big,
giant career,

41:41.000 --> 41:44.080
but I never want to go anywhere
without you.

41:44.080 --> 41:48.710
♪ Human beings let you down ♪

41:48.710 --> 41:52.380
You are my home.

41:52.380 --> 41:54.920
♪♪

41:54.920 --> 41:58.380
And you are my heart.

41:58.380 --> 42:03.580
Alex Karev,
will you marry me?

42:03.580 --> 42:05.040
[ Laughs ]

42:05.040 --> 42:07.500
They can become smoother,
softer.

42:07.500 --> 42:09.080
-Wait, so that's a...
-It's a yes.

42:09.080 --> 42:10.210
[ Laughing ] ...a yes.

42:10.210 --> 42:11.790
It's a hell yes.

42:11.790 --> 42:14.080
And some scars
can even fade away.

42:14.080 --> 42:16.000
♪ They'll let you down ♪

42:29.120 --> 42:37.540
♪♪

